            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has slightly thickened, add the <strong>crispy Fable mushrooms</strong> and stir it all together until everything is coated in sauce – these are your <strong>crispy chilli Fable mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
